modShortDescription: Sets parameters in items.xml to produce overpowered pickaxe and speedier wrench.
modDescription:
Sets parameters in items.xml to produce overpowered [pickaxe](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-tools/) and speedier wrench.

**[Download](https://github.com/pahbi/7DTD_Modlets/raw/main/superPickaxe.zip)**

The forum topic of the mod is [here](https://community.7daystodie.com/topic/26048-a20-modlets-lotl-perk-fast-plant-growth-super-iron-pickaxe/).
